// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-3732 — Mass File Rename (stormous)
// Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: ecb2f99f-8737-5416-aa49-20195299f811

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
